
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SourceCode Getter</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styling */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000, #1a1a2e); /* Subtle dark blue gradient */
            color: #a020f0; /* Purple text */
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #a020f0; /* Solid purple */
        }

        h4 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #a020f0; /* Soft pink */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Form Styling */
        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px; /* Space between input and button */
        }

        /* Bigger Input Field */
        input {
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 16px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border: 2px solid #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            outline: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
            background: #222;
            color: #fff;
        }

        input:focus {
            border-color: #6fa3ef; /* Soft Blue */
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 12px rgba(111, 163, 239, 0.8);
        }

        /* Subtle Button */
        button {
            background: #5cdb95;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 24px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin-top: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(92, 219, 149, 0.5);
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #4cad85;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(92, 219, 149, 0.8);
        }




        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            input {
                width: 90%;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="container">
        <h2>Fetch Your Favorite website's Code</h2>
        <h4>You can get code of any website in just one click!</h4>
        <h4>In the result endpoint Pass the url as a variable name and set the value of you're desired url address of the website</h4>
        <h5>Ex: https://localhost/result?url=http://address of the photo</h5>
    </div>
    <p>Your mission: Find the secret flag by exploiting an SSRF vulnerability.</p>
    <p>There is a hidden server running here in different port number, you need to get the flag from /flag endpoint</p>

</body>
</html>
